data.description: Beautiful 3-2/1 townhouse in desired neighborhood of Venetian Parc! Situated in a friendly community across from its clubhouse which includes: business area, gym, pool, covered bbq & playground, close to schools, highways, and hospitals. Home has been freshly painted in a serene calming light gray color, Zebra window treatments, Brand new A/C unit only a few months old, Master & Junior Suite include California closets, Large ceramic tiles on 1st floor & laminated wood floor on stairs & 2nd level. Paved backyard with a gate to common access areas, 1 car garage with tankless water heater and Stainless Steel energy efficient appliances. The features in this townhome is what sets it apart from the rest. Owner-occupied showing by appointment only call LA. Bring your final & best offer.
